where where you 25 years ago right now .... i know where i was ....
this is an awesome recording of an awesome show of an awesome tour .... 
i love this source ... 
it has some  nice bottom end ... very good recording.
the whole 1st set is quite solid....  as is the second set extravaganza  .... 
1983 was a very good year ...
thank you for this. 
very much appreciated .
day job and althea 83 isnt rushed but its fast
